org.eeml.math.expr

Class Root

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eeml.math.expr.Root
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable

    public class Root
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable
    This class mainly implements the math expression square root. The class allows users to calculate and express the square root of an integer that can be displayed in a appealing way. Maintained by EEML. see more on eeml.github.io
    Since:
    v1.0.0
